Take a kadai and pour oil in it and heat it .

Take one boul and break the eggs in it and remove white shell from boul and add chilly powder, salt, ginger garlic paste(optional).

Now mix it well.Then it become has OMLETE.

when the kadai get heated pour the OMLETE in that let fry it.Fry the both sides.

NOW THE OMLETE IS READY.SERVE IT .